### 1. input the summary file generated by samtools idxstats
### 2. sum the reads mapped to each mag and then divide this sum by total contig length of the community
### 3. To determine the relative abundance of each MAG, divide the value obtained for each MAG in step 2 by the total sum of all values obtained in step 2 across all MAGs. 
